WEBVTT

00:00:06.042 --> 00:00:09.740
This is a kindergarten
we designed in 2007.

00:00:10.111 --> 00:00:14.036
We made this kindergarten 
to be a circle.

00:00:14.036 --> 00:00:17.178
It's a kind of endless circulation
on top of the roof.

00:00:17.179 --> 00:00:19.699
If you are a parent,

00:00:19.699 --> 00:00:23.663
you know that kids love
to keep making circles.

00:00:24.793 --> 00:00:27.600
This is how the rooftop looks.

